snippet.title: Elements Destiny - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Elements Destiny is a retro-JRPG inspired by SNES era. It features an emotional story with a diverse cast of characters, a thrilling soundtrack with over 100 Tracks and stunning pixel art visuals. Play the game at Gamescom 2024 in Hall 10.2 at the Indie Arena Booth.

Steam:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1635500/Elements_Destiny/
GOG: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1635500/Elements_Destiny/
Website: https://www.elementsdestiny.de/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/GameEDofficial
Discord: https://discord.gg/ZKjdNYKPNP
